---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Investment Counsel">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-text-muted space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">

        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted/60">Published: 17 February 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">1. General Provisions</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Policy (hereinafter the "Policy") sets out the approach to the processing and protection of personal data of individuals visiting the "Investment Counsel" website (hereinafter the "Website").</p>
        <p>The Policy has been prepared in accordance with Federal Law No. 152-FZ of 27 July 2006 "On Personal Data" and other applicable regulations of the Russian Federation.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">2. Operator</h2>
        <p>The operator of the Website is its owner (hereinafter the "Operator"). Contact details are provided in the "Contact" section of the Website.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">3. Collection of Personal Data</h2>
        <p>The Website <strong>does not collect personal data</strong> from visitors. The Website does not use:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Feedback or registration forms;</li>
          <li>Analytics or tracking systems (Google Analytics, Yandex.Metrica, etc.);</li>
          <li>Cookies set by the Website.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The Website provides links to external communication channels (Telegram, WhatsApp, email, LinkedIn). When following these links, data processing is handled by the respective services in accordance with their own privacy policies.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">4. Hosting Technical Data</h2>
        <p>The Website is hosted on GitHub Pages. The hosting provider may automatically record standard server data (IP address, browser type, access time) to ensure service availability. The Operator has no access to this data and does not use it.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">5. User Rights</h2>
        <p>Since the Website does not collect or process personal data, there are no grounds for exercising data subject rights under Federal Law No. 152-FZ in relation to the Operator.</p>
        <p>For any questions, you may use the contact details provided on the Website.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">6. Changes to the Policy</h2>
        <p>The Operator reserves the right to amend this Policy. The current version is published on this page.</p>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-secondary/20">
          <a href="/TaxSpecialistLandingEN/" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-medium">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
